{"tid":1587623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到文宣組入］文宣新方向","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T13:15:34.000Z","uid":16946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f08b9b84d5c4884fd00f58ca730aae11d0ea180","tid":1587623,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"依家嘅文宣大部份係黑警/藍絲罪證或者口號類型嘅宣傳<br />\n<br />\n呢啲文宣的確可以鞏固我方立場同拉攏民意 吸引咗好多上年紀嘅人睇<br />\n<br />\n但事到如今 <span style=\"color: red;\">大部份人立場已定</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁成功拉攏咗更多人入我地陣營之後 應該點做？</span><br />\n<br />\n心態變黃之後下一步就係<span style=\"color: red;\">行動都要變黃</span>！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令佢地變成我地嘅行動力！<br />\n</span><br />\n好多上咗年紀嘅 即使係深黃 都好少可會上前線 佢地有時想幫都唔知可以做啲咩<br />\n所以我哋<span style=\"color: red;\">必須要進一步令抗爭融入生活</span><br />\n<br />\n行動文宣黎講 除咗現有嘅週末行動嘅文宣外 我地可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">加多啲指南/教學類型嘅文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">指南類：</span></strong></span><br />\n- 罷食list<br />\n- 罷買list<br />\n- 美心旗下商鋪list<br />\n- 港鐵商場list<br />\n- TVB廣告商list <br />\netc<br />\n總之所有要抵制嘅 都大大力宣傳 <span style=\"color: red;\">可以貼喺連儂牆或者商場</span> 等佢地喺日常生活都可以增加我方嘅bargaining power<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">教學類：</span></strong></span><br />\n- 如何用Twitter retweet對我方有利嘅資訊<br />\n可參考：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1r95av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1r95av.jpg&h=32a79ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 如何用Reddit/Quora留言<br />\n- 如何用Facebook喺TVB廣告商派嬲同留言<br />\n可參考此fb page：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fde6d5be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\n<br />\n總之所有網戰嘅參軍方法 都可以整啲簡單教學<br />\n(香港人好少用tweeter reddit呢類大型外國網站 <span style=\"color: red;\">主要都淨係喺ig story同fb度post文宣 </span>所以即使係做比同溫層嘅都好有用)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">未開twitter reddit quora accout嘅巴絲快啲開返個！</span>國際戰線係大量五毛！<br />\n仲有929就係全球抗共大遊行 呢幾日大家快啲上twitter reddit煲煲佢！<br />\n<br />\n最後想講<br />\n唔好以為有其他人做緊你就唔洗做<span style=\"color: red;\"> 每一條戰線都需要人幫手 大家儘量做得幾多得幾多</span> 唔好睇少自己一分力 二百萬人一人一啖口水都浸撚死班黑警<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\nUseful Links:<br />\nTwitter軍tg group<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=4bcca877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n抵制TVB廣告商fb group<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fde6d5be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a>"},{"pid":"c62e81174eddd041ca8d60a47a2a0b6518ce30bb","tid":1587623,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cca5e9f72dbec476245a740b20444d708a293e53","tid":1587623,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9f6535b8c31885a0e22f2ab18b9477df212f78a","tid":1587623,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"自推二十次"},{"pid":"0a5fa5d9ea1c02ac255bf364c74233f6281c1dcf","tid":1587623,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"e3c7475fea90a677e9731f94585726045e7ff05e","tid":1587623,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"2/20"}